			<p>At the Hofstra University Club on Sunday, April 10th 2010, Brooklyn College alumni from all over Long Island were treated to Conservatory of Music alumnus Yotam Ginzburgâ€™s virtuoso performance on classical guitar.  The event was held in honor of Brooklyn College President Karen L. Gould, who recognized and thanked Mr. Ginzburg from the podium.  Many alumni and guests found their way over to him during the afternoon to listen more closely and to chat with him about music and Brooklyn College.  A lovely afternoon was made even more special by the gracious presence and superb talents of Mr. Ginzburg.<br />
